HEADWORD: Post-tympanic
<hw>Post`-tym*pan"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>post-</ets> + <ets>tympanic</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Anat.)</fld>
